## ThreadID.toBytes() method

toBytes returns the byte representation of an ID. The output of bytes can be parsed back into an ID with fromBytes.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
toBytes(): Buffer;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

Buffer
